    public static final class VKList.ReflectParser<D extends VKApiModel>
extends java.lang.Object
implements VKList.Parser<D>
    Parser list items using reflection mechanism. To use an object class must have a public constructor that accepts JSONObject. If, during the creation of the object constructor will throw any exception, the element will not be added to the list.
